r3070 | joeshaw | 2006-12-04 14:41:17 -0500 (Mon, 04 Dec 2006) | 15 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/Util/Conf.cs
   M /trunk/beagled/BeagleDaemon.cs
   M /trunk/beagled/Makefile.am
   A /trunk/beagled/beagled-autostart.desktop
